{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Apz68A9RkGcY95VDiijqh3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear: `es-0` has discovered itself but cannot discover `es-1` and `es-2`. The `discovery.seed_hosts: [\"es-internal\"]` is resolving but maybe not finding the other nodes yet, or there's a transport SSL issue.\n\nThe message says:\n- \"have discovered [es-0...]\"\n- \"discovery will continue using [] from hosts providers and [{es-0}...] from last-known cluster state\"\n- \"discovery will continue using [] from hosts providers\" - this means the `es-internal` hostname is resolving to no peers (only itself or nothing for the other nodes)\n- \nWith a StatefulSet, pods start sequentially—es-0 must be Ready before es-1 and es-2 even begin launching. Since es-0's readiness probe is failing, the other pods are stuck waiting. I need to set `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` so all three pods start at once instead of this sequential bottleneck.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":811,"cache_read_input_tokens":39212,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":811},"output_tokens":23,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e75b3fab-749e-4aeb-968c-fec95891c9a6","uuid":"f4e772a5-e7f9-46fd-90a6-02d77ba5353c","request_id":"req_011Cc8tv3Bd56gPF6QrRyHVZ"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Apz68A9RkGcY95VDiijqh3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The problem is clear: the StatefulSet uses sequential pod startup by default, so `es-0` waits for Ready before `es-1`/`es-2` start — but `es-0` can't form a cluster alone. I need `podManagementPolicy: Parallel`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":811,"cache_read_input_tokens":39212,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":811},"output_tokens":23,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e75b3fab-749e-4aeb-968c-fec95891c9a6","uuid":"0757df0b-a324-42d2-b7cd-513074a1ebd7","request_id":"req_011Cc8tv3Bd56gPF6QrRyHVZ"}
